{"tid":1649793,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"手足，不割蓆，可提點呀","createTime":"2019-10-12T18:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T18:36:49.000Z","uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e5837aa59e81917c53780b61b873e813b6e30c10","tid":1649793,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:31:42.000Z","msg":"我明白時間同地點方面都唔應該切蛋糕慶祝<br />\n<br />\n但記住大家行左四個月<br />\n全靠手足們不割蓆不篤灰不分化<br />\n佢一定有錯，可以提點<br />\n<br />\n如果對方有認錯嘅話大家就唔好再針著<br />\n<br />\n亦都希望其他食緊花生嘅人諗下<br />\n點解咁多人有咁大反應<br />\n唔好笑完就算<br />\n自己亦都唔好犯同樣嘅錯<br />\n<br />\n聽日十八區見"},{"pid":"07dd5e1b15389a786aee5f4af73231766e2cb3ed","tid":1649793,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d451c7964fe8b0f7e8a20f0d7093fcaa3b39ca","tid":1649793,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:32:10.000Z","msg":"不分化"},{"pid":"9a61d0455dd4f89ff761a1a5a0f451f123fe4d27","tid":1649793,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:32:51.000Z","msg":"不割蓆"},{"pid":"ba685ce8b9ff93a1ea43188a3d56f3339960fcb6","tid":1649793,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:33:01.000Z","msg":"不篤灰"},{"pid":"6d563ed0d01bfa392dcc32066f30a71a57febcc9","tid":1649793,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:33:53.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n[品蔥建議] [拋磚引玉] 如何偽裝成一名合格的&ldquo;愛國港人&rdquo;（藍絲）？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"65f4ce24d9a6833ae5a3544b0825f4fd2d9b0458","tid":1649793,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":